===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|graffe|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|greffe||stylus|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|graphium||stylus|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|γραφείον|lang=grc}}, from {{term|γράφειν||to write|lang=grc}}; probably akin to English {{term|carve|lang=en}}. So named from the resemblance of a scion or shoot to a pointed pencil. Compare [[graphic]], [[grammar]].

