===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A small [[shoot]] or [[scion]] of a tree inserted in another tree, the [[stock]] of which is to [[support]] and [[nourish]] it. The two [[unite]] and become one tree, but the graft determines the kind of [[fruit]].
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A [[branch]] or [[portion]] of a tree growing from such a shoot.
# {{context|surgery|countable|lang=en}} A portion of living [[tissue]] used in the operation of [[autoplasty]].
# {{context|uncountable|colloquial|lang=en}} Effort needed for doing hard [[work]].
# {{context|uncountable|slang|lang=en}} A criminal's special branch of practice
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} [[illicit|Illicit]] [[profit]] by [[corrupt]] [[means]], especially in public life.
# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} [[corruption|Corruption]] in [[official]] life.
# {{context|countable|lang=en}} A [[con job]].
# {{context|countable|slang|lang=en}} A [[cut]] of the [[take]] (money).
# {{context|uncountable|US|politics|lang=en}} A [[bribe]], especially on an ongoing basis.
